						<summary>

						<p>Slab in the maṭha (on two sides). </p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">1652 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records a grant of land and certain privileges to Chenna-Virayya of Kallūra-maṭha in the presence of the <hi rend="italic">gauda,</hi> Kulkarni, Seṭṭi, Chaudhari and others.</p>						

						<p>It is dated śaka 1572 [wrong for 1574] Nandana, Vaiśākha, adhika-ashṭami, Wednesday. It corresponds to 1652 A.D., April 21. The month Vaiśākha was adhika.</p>						

						</summary>
