<!--<h4>Front side.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrī śakhe sālivāha
<lb n="2" break="no"/>na 1572 neya naṁda
<lb n="3" break="no"/>nanāma saṁvatsarada
<lb n="4"/>vaiśākha ba Ādhika Ā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṣṭami budhavāradalū
<lb n="6"/>śrīmatu kalura maṭhada
<lb n="7"/>caṁnavirayage (divāli)
<lb n="8"/>vā gauḍa kulakarṇi vā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>malagauḍa seṭi (ca)udariga
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ḷu muṁtāda samasta pra
<lb n="11" break="no"/>jegaḷu darṁma sākṣi
<lb n="12" break="no"/>yāgi baradukoṭha
<lb n="13"/>dāna patrada sāsanau
<lb n="14"/><unclear>Adake</unclear> nimage māṁnya
</p>

<!--<h4>Back side.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="15" break="no"/>da hola bijavari
<lb n="16"/>khaṁ 82 koṭu yidheU
<lb n="17"/>muṁde staḷa bharitana gu
<lb n="18" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> vaṁdake kha 2 busare bhū
<lb n="19" break="no"/>vaṁdake kha 6 vidake kha 1 vaṁ
<lb n="20" break="no"/>dake <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> dinake yari 50
<lb n="21"/>yiṣṭu koṭhu yideU yi
<lb n="22" break="no"/>dake tapidare kāsili gō
<lb n="23" break="no"/>hatya māḍida dōsake hō
<lb n="24" break="no"/>haru bhāvi payiṁbhu
<lb n="25" break="no"/>mi(naṁ) koṭhuyideU
<lb n="26"/>dharma sākṣi <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

